   * @link [API Docs](https://tanstack.com/table/v8/docs/api/features/pagination#setpagination)
   * @link [Guide](https://tanstack.com/table/v8/docs/guide/pagination)
   */
  setPagination: (updater: Updater<PaginationState>) => void
